long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Seefunnel Chrome Extension - Effortless Lead Generation

Find Email Addresses and Leads in One Click!
Seefunnel makes lead generation simple and efficient. With just one click, you can find email addresses directly from LinkedIn profiles or websites, and easily add them to your free lead list on the Seefunnel dashboard.

LinkedIn Search
Looking to find a prospect's email address on LinkedIn? Simply open their profile and click "Find Leads." Our system will search all available sources and retrieve the lead's email address if it's available.

Website Search
When browsing a website, click "Find Leads" to uncover contact details like email addresses and phone numbers associated with the domain. The system identifies potential users and provides their details to streamline your outreach.

Start building your lead lists today with Seefunnel Chrome Extension!
